{"lemma":"عَيْباتُ","slug":"عَيْباتُ","root":"ع.#.ب","root_slug":"ع-_-ب","root_link":"/words/roots/ع-_-ب","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n31148","n31153","n31154"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B9%D9%8E%D9%8A%D9%92%D8%A8%D8%A7%D8%AA%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"defect, fault, shortcoming"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"imperfection, incompleteness"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Instance noun from عَابَ (ʕāba, “to be defective”)."},"ipa":["/ʕaj.ba/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n31148","headword_ar":"عيّبهُ","root":"Eyb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see 1, in two places.       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ey~b","text_ar":"عيّب"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He made,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"prepared,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"took for himself, what is called an"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eayobap","text_ar":"عَيْبَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O.)"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n31153","headword_ar":"عَيْبَةٌ","root":"Eyb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see the next preceding paragraph.       -A2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A receptacle in which clothes are put:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a receptable of skin,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"leather, in which goods,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"utensils, are put:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zabiyl","text_ar":"زَبِيل"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"receptacle like a basket"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of skin,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"leather"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in which reaped corn is conveyed to the threshing-floor:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a thing like the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xariyTap","text_ar":"خَرِيطَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of skin,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"leather:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ham p. 352:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it has loops with which it is closed and fastened by the insertion of one into another:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(see 4 in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$rj","text_ar":"شرج"},{"kind":"text","text":":)] pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EiyabN","text_ar":"عِيَبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EiyaAbN","text_ar":"عِيَابٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EayobaAtN","text_ar":"عَيْبَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, O, K.) ―         -b2-  Hence, (A,) (tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"depositary of"},{"kind":"text","text":"one's"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"secret"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"secrets"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (A, O, K) and it is used as a sing and a pl.:] one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa Eayobapu fulaAn","text_ar":"هُوَ عَيْبَةُ فُلَان"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He is the depositary of the secret"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"secrets"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of such a one:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A:) and it is said in a trad.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA^anoSaAru","text_ar":"الاَنْصَارُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kari$iY waEayobatiY","text_ar":"كَرِشِى وَعَيْبَتِى"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, TA) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The Anṣár are my intimates, and the depositary of my secret"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"secrets"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA. [See also other explanations in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kr$","text_ar":"كرش"},{"kind":"text","text":".]) And [in like manner]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEyaAbu","text_ar":"العيَابُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is used as meaning (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The breasts."},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the hearts:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K:) for, as the Arab deposits in his"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eyobap","text_ar":"عيْبَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"the best of his goods, or utensils, and of his clothes so he conceals in his breast his meat particular secrets, which may not be divulge. (O, * TA) Hence, (TA,) a poet says,"},{"kind":"quote","text":"wakaAdato EiyaAbu Alwud~i min~aA waminokumu\n                      \n                     \n                        waA_ino qiyla A^abonaA='u AlEumuwmapi taSofaru"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And our and your depositories of love, although it be said"},{"kind":"text","text":"that we and you are"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the children of paternal uncles, were near to becoming and"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (O, TA:) by"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EyAb Alwd~","text_ar":"عياب الودّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"he means their breasts. (TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bayonanaA wabayonahumo EayobapN makofuwfapN","text_ar":"بَيْنَنَا وَبَيْنَهُمْ عَيْبَةٌ مَكْفُوفَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", a phrase in the treaty of El-Hodeybiyeh. means (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Between us and them,"},{"kind":"text","text":"in respect of this peace, is [determined that there shall be, in each party.]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a breast bound to fulfil the terms of this writing."},{"kind":"text","text":"like the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eybp","text_ar":"عيبة"},{"kind":"text","text":"that is closed and fastened by its loops over its contents,] clear of secret enmity, and perfidy, and deceit: (IAar, O, * TA:) or, accord. to some, as related by Sh,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"evil between us"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and them"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"shall be"},{"kind":"text","text":"[as it were]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tied up,"},{"kind":"text","text":"like as the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eybp","text_ar":"عيبة"},{"kind":"text","text":"is tied up: or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"there shall be mutual reconciliation, and abstaining from war, like that kind of friendship that subsists between sincere friends who confide in each other."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Az, TA. [See also art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kf","text_ar":"كف"},{"kind":"text","text":".]) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ealayoka biEayonatika","text_ar":"عَلَيْكَ بِعَيْنَتِكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", said by 'Áïsheh to 'Omar on an occasion of his blaming her, means (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Busy thyself with thine own family,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wife,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and let me alone. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","O","K","TA","A"]},{"entry_id":"n31154","headword_ar":"عُيَبَةٌ","root":"Eyb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eay~aAbN","text_ar":"عَيَّابٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}